<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Ka Pa In Vangsakna</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Gitloh suoka pat pawtin,
 Buoina khel gamnuom ah;
 Ka Pa In Vangsakna In nuom achun,
 Aw lungngaih thuok ta lodi'n,
 Kumsawt kipahna la sa'i tiu.

[V2]
 Zuon ingka kumsawt kipah na'ng,
 Hukdam leh angel vamte hawn;
 Ka Hukdampa a pak nau chuh,
 Tun ding kinem in ka thil hi.

[V3]
 2. Lei dogalte a hung lien,
 Lungkham lungzinna hin;
 Meipi bangin ei hun tuomvel ta ie,
 Aw Lalpa ei panpih in,
 Na angsung nuom ka hun zuon ie.

[V4]
 3. Na angsung ah ei paiin,
 Lei dogal hat lakah;
 Na Thagau Thiengtho thilbawl theihna chun,
 Aw Lalpa ei panpih in.
 Na na chu hun sem zing ing ka.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>172</hymn_number>
</song>